headline: RBC Capital Markets Joins ICE Clear Credit as an FCM to Expand CDS Client Clearing Services
summary: ATLANTA & NEW YORK, June 26, 2025--Intercontinental Exchange, Inc. (NYSE: ICE), a leading global provider of technology and data, today announced that RBC Capital Markets, LLC (RBC), a subsidiary of Royal Bank of Canada, has joined ICE Clear Credit, the world’s premier clearinghouse for credit default swaps, as a Futures Commission Merchant (FCM) clearing participant.
